app, ss = basic_ss
test_client = SocketIOTestClient(app, ss.socketio, namespace=ss.namespace)
ss.send_subscription_fail = Mock()
test_client.emit('message', json.dumps({'type': 'unknown message type',
    'payload': 'foo', 'query': 'query test{ testString }', 'variables':
    'baz'}), namespace=ss.namespace)
ss.send_subscription_fail.assert_called_once()
assert ss.send_subscription_fail.call_args[0][1] == {'errors':
    'Invalid message type'}
